data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the desirable River Park community in Mount Holly! This stunning 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home, built in 2021, blends modern luxury with comfortable living. Upon entering, you're greeted with loads of natural light and an open floor plan. The bright and airy living room creates an inviting atmosphere that is spacious yet cozy. The well-equipped kitchen has ample storage and counter space plus a dining area and an island to make entertaining a delight. Upstairs you'll find the primary suite featuring a generously sized bedroom, a walk-in closet, and en-suite bathroom with dual sinks. Two additional bedrooms, a loft aea, and a full bathroom provide plenty of space for whatever you need. Schedule a showing today!
